NOTE ON OPTIONAL CGO COMPONENTS

The default (pure-Go) build of FluxDocs is MIT-licensed as above. Optional
features compiled behind build tags depend on third-party libraries under
different licenses, and binaries built with those tags are subject to them:

  - build tag `mupdf`  — links MuPDF (AGPL-3.0 / commercial). Binaries built
                         with this tag are governed by the AGPL-3.0.
  - build tag `ocr`    — links Tesseract (Apache-2.0).

Do not enable these tags unless you accept the corresponding license terms.
See .claude/SECURITY.md (section 6) and docs/spec.md (§18.4) for details.
